In the Matter of Frank J. Caffery, Respondent, v. James R. Lawley et al., as Commissioners of the Board of Elections of Erie County, Respondents, and Patricia A. Griffin et al., Appellants. Argued May 27, 1964; decided May 27, 1964. *769Dean E. Higgins for appellants. Harold M. Halpern for Frank J. Caffery, respondent.

No appearance for remaining respondents.

Order affirmed, without costs; no opinion.

Chief Judge Desmond and Judges Dye, Fuld, Van Voorhis, Burke, Scileppi and Hamm*.

Designated pursuant to section 2 of article VI of the State Constitution in the temporary absence of Judge Bergan.
